      <title>摩纳哥批评瑞士宝盛银行对 1.74 亿美元交易的客户管控不力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/julius-baer-criticized-by-monaco-for-poor-controls-on-client-money</link>
